name: The Meeting Place
description: This artwork is about how to Make Myself Work even I’m not in the Mood. The days I lack motivation or are unable to arouse my usual interest in things I normally enjoy begin to rest my mind and body. In the end I realized that sometimes periods of feeling like this are perfectly normal. And then I embrace the feeling that I'm experiencing and just do it as usual, rather than procrastinating on things that can be a full-fledged addiction. I beat procrastination and get things done even when I don't feel like working.
